content:
A sales overview dashboard is a great way for teams to collaborate on opportunities because it provides a complete picture of your pipeline. Dashboard widgets already link to source reports, so you can get more details. Link to other destinations to take action on the data.

Available in: Lightning Experience, Essentials, Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions

After giving dashboard viewers insights about their business, drive them to take the next step by providing one-click access to Salesforce records or websites.
Dashboard builders can link dashboard widgets to Salesforce records or other websites. Visit a link to act on dashboard insights!
title: Linking Dashboard Widgets in Salesforce
